----------Explain and demonstrate ways to debug Hybrid Mobile-----------
----------------Applications Running on a real device-------------------


Ionic makes it possible to debug through your browser using sockets and ports from which you
phone communicates with your browser allowing you to see the console and debug live.

 once you run your device using : ionic run android

 you can open chrome and navigate to: chrome://inspect/#devices

 there you should be able to see your device and access the console.